    <stitle>BRAKE COMPONENTS: This Service Manual Section should be used for reference only. For more current service
        information on all components go to the Bendix website from the ISIS Suppliers menu and refer to the Service
        Data Sheets. - QR-N QUICK RELEASE VALVE - REMOVE
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="IDcomponent" graphiccount="0">
        <title>REMOVE</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Park the vehicle on a level surface. Block the wheels.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Drain all air brake system reservoirs.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Identify, mark and disconnect all air lines from the valve.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove all tubing or hose fittings from the valve.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the valve mounting hardware and the valve.</para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
